OOC: Yes, I thuroughly enjoyed invasion as well. rAuq, Blot has arrived,
and Menasor has just been kidnapped.

BIC:

Blot swaggered up to the rest, after taking a long look at Menasor being
attacked. "Blot here, what we do now?" he asked, truly confused by the
situation.
